|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[URL@0 as URL, count(Int64(1))@1 as PageViews]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
